The App communicates with a remote directory server (the “KnC Directory Server”), which has been produced by and is the property of KnC Group AB (“KnC”). KnC is referred to as “us”, “we”, and “our” in this EULA. We are a company registered in Sweden, with company number 556931-9725. Our registered office is at Birger Jarlsgatan 33, 111 45 Stockholm, Sweden (“KNC”).  You are permitted to use the KnC Directory Server in accordance with this EULA. 

