6.	BACKING UP 
6.1	The App gives you the option to backup your Bitcoin wallet seed to external third party providers (“Backup”).  WE STRONGLY RECOMMEND THAT YOU BACKUP YOUR SEED.  If you Backup and your phone or the App is lost or damaged, you will be able to recover your seed from the Backup.
6.2	Backup may require you to enter additional passwords or undertake additional security measures.
6.3	Backup is subject to the terms of the third party backup providers and we do not make any warranty, undertaking or representation in respect of such providers.  
6.4	IT IS UP TO YOU TO TAKE WHATEVER SECURITY MEASURES YOU THINK NECESSARY TO ENSURE THAT YOUR BACKUP IS SECURE.  WE ARE NOT LIABLE FOR ANY IMPROPER USE OF YOUR BACKUP BY YOU OR ANY OTHER PERSON.

